org.bytedeco.cpu_features

Class list_cpu_features

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.cpu_features.list_cpu_features

  • @Properties(inherit=cpu_features.class,
            value=@Platform(executable="list_cpu_features"))
public class list_cpu_features
extends Object
    With this class, we can extract easily the list_cpu_features program ready for execution. For example, we can print the CPU features from Java in a portable fashion this way: 
    
     String list_cpu_features = Loader.load(org.bytedeco.cpu_features.list_cpu_features.class);
     ProcessBuilder pb = new ProcessBuilder(list_cpu_features);
     pb.inheritIO().start().waitFor();
    Author:
    Samuel Audet
